nodes.text: The Kashyyyk Senatorial Delegation was the political body that represented the planet Kashyyyk and the rest of the Mytaranor sector during the last decades of the Galactic Republic. It consisted of a Wookiee senator and his or her aides. Despite their short tempers, Wookiee senators were respected for their firm sense of justice. The Trandoshans, another species from the Mytaranor sector, were resentful of the fact that Wookiees alone would represent their common area of space in the pan-galactic political arena.
